Class KeyValue<A,B>

  • Object
    • uk.aspyr.stl4j.Tuple
      • uk.aspyr.stl4j.KeyValue<A,B>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Tuple>, ValueKey<A>, ValueValue<B>

    public final class KeyValue<A,B>
extends Tuple
implements ValueKey<A>, ValueValue<B>
    A tuple of two elements, with positions 0 and 1 renamed as "key" and "value", respectively.

    Darren Bell
